OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTenants left with damp     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhomes after 2018 storm     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A woman has said her flat is so cold   
OL,6, and damp she sometimes goes to bed as  
OL,7, early as six o'clock to stay warm.     
OL,9,FDenise Jones said there was persistent 
OL,10,Fblack mould in her bathroom and found  
OL,11,Ftoadstools growing in her kitchen.     
OL,13,FHer landlord, Bron Afon housing        
OL,14,Fassociation, said it would "continue to
OL,15,Fwork" with her to resolve any issues.  
OL,17,FThe Welsh government has written to    
OL,18,Fsocial landlords "seeking urgent       
OL,19,Fassurance" on how they monitor and     
OL,20,Frespond to damp and mould issues.      
